author: Buddha
message: Your work is to discover your work and then with all your heart to give yourself to it.
title: Thought of the day

author: Epictetus
message: It's not what happens to you, but how you react to it that matters.
title: Thought of the day

author: Woody Guthrie
message: Take it easy, but take it.
title: Thought of the day

author: Benjamin Disraeli
message: Never apologize for showing feeling. When you do so, you apologize for truth.
title: Thought of the day
